│ IC: Replacing   %sel = select i1 %cmp1, i1 %cmp2, i1 false   │
│     with   %0 = icmp eq i32 %popcnt, 1                       │
│ ```                                                          │
│ This pinpoints the exact transformation that introduces the  │
│ incorrect behavior.                                          │
│                                                              │
