│ aggressive optimization that did not correctly handle the    │
│ `poison` value produced by `ctpop(0)` when `range` metadata  │
│ is present. The final patch correctly and conservatively     │
│ checks for conditions where this transformation is safe,     │
│ fixing the bug without introducing regressions.              │
