│ optimization is only applied if it can be definitively       │
│ proven that `ctpop(0)` will not result in a `poison` value.  │
│ This is true if there is no `range` metadata, or if the      │
│ `range` metadata explicitly includes zero as its lower       │
│ bound. In all other cases, including malformed metadata, the │
│ transformation is safely skipped.                            │
